dcterms:description: RESIDE is a large-scale synthetic dataset including indoor and outdoor scenes, containing five subsets: Indoor Training Set (ITS), Outdoor Training Set (OTS), Synthetic Objective Testing Set (SOTS), Real World task-driven Testing Set (RTTS), and Hybrid Subjective Testing Set (HSTS).
dcterms:title: RESIDE

dcterms:description: HazeRD is an outdoor scene dataset and benchmark for single image dehazing, specifically designed to evaluate dehazing algorithms in real-world scenarios.
dcterms:title: HazeRD

dcterms:description: DENSE-HAZE is a benchmark for image dehazing that includes dense-haze and haze-free images, aimed at evaluating dehazing algorithms.
dcterms:title: DENSE-HAZE
